        6
      ],
      "right": "275px"
    },
    {
      "width": "377px",
      "text": "רבא ברוך <i data-commentator=\"Shiltei HaGiborim\" data-label=\"א\" data-order=\"1\"></i>רופא חנם <i data-commentator=\"Chiddushei Anshei Shem\" data-label=\"א\" data-order=\"1\"></i><i data-commentator=\"Mishneh Torah, Prayer and the Priestly Blessing\" data-label=\"⚬\"></i><i data-commentator=\"Sefer Mitzvot Gadol\" data-label=\"⚬\"></i><i data-commentator=\"Tur\" data-label=\"⚬\"></i>(דף ס:)",
